---
title: Seared Flank Steak & Garlic Aioli with Cucumber Salad & Fries
description: Fire up the grill and grab your apron - it’s steak night! On the menu tonight we have flank steak, the lean and flavourful cut that packs a punch. Let’s keep the sides basic and let the star of the show shine - golden fries, fresh salad and a creamy Dijon mayo are the perfect sidekicks.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
